{"tid":2463640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【緬甸抗爭】軍方以「格殺勿論」對付平民　四分之一死者遭爆頭","createTime":"2021-03-27T01:07:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T02:17:00.000Z","uid":271829,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"93eedd28c2c27f65339529cbd2b0a0fa7fad2663","tid":2463640,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T01:07:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/9rGK_qSJ_rSsjPZI8hdtGvh2EZA=/760x506/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/COC4R35XRZB7NNEBFSZAV24M5E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9rGK_qSJ_rSsjPZI8hdtGvh2EZA%3D%2F760x506%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCOC4R35XRZB7NNEBFSZAV24M5E.jpg&h=82b683d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n緬甸示威民眾將受傷者抬離現場。法新社<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n緬甸軍方鎮壓反政變示威者的武力升級，估計已造成逾300名平民死亡，死者有近90%是被擊斃，25%人頭部中彈，令人質疑軍警蓄意向示威者頭部開槍。學者形容近日緬甸連串事件，讓人聯想起當地過往多次政變，感嘆歷史在重演。<br />\n<br />\n緬甸官方及民間對於示威死亡人數的統計多有出入，緬軍周二（23日）表示截至當天有164名示威者及9名軍方人員被槍殺，與民間指的200多人不同。當地民間團體「政治犯援助聯盟」（AAPP）統計就顯示，截至本周四有320名示威者死亡，近3,000人被捕。<br />\n<br />\nAAPP統計示威死者資料，發現大部份是男性，36%年齡是24歲或以下，且最少25%人是頭部中槍而死，批評「有違人道的罪行每天都有出現」。國際特赦組織形容，軍方正運用「格殺勿論」戰術對付平民，藉此壓制示威。緬甸軍方否認使用過度武力，強調一切行動符合國際標準，又指緬甸國家安全面臨威脅。<br />\n<br />\n美國等西方國家近日開始制裁緬甸軍方高層，不少東南亞國家亦批評緬甸以致命武器攻擊示威者。美國喬治城大學（Georgetown University）教授斯坦伯格（David I. Steinberg）形容緬甸的歷史不斷以相近的方式重演，即使過去多次失敗，仍會繼續以往的做法。<br />\n<br />\n斯坦伯格指，緬甸自1948年獨立以來，已發生4次政變，分別是1958年的第一次政變，由軍方暫時接管權力；1962年軍方推翻昂山將軍的政府，正式確立軍政府統治；1988年軍方再介入鎮壓「8888」民主運動；以及今次推翻翁山蘇姬領導的文人政府。他形容儘管緬甸領導層經歷以往政變的後果，卻仍然讓歷史重演，而政變次數雖不及鄰國泰國，卻比泰國血腥。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210327/SINCYW5KGNCYNB5U7XRE6AXLKI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210327%2FSINCYW5KGNCYNB5U7XRE6AXLKI%2F&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWh1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=e13f97bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210327%2FSINCYW5KGNCYNB5U7XRE6AXLKI%2F&h=a2b6d924\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210327/SINCYW5KGNCYNB5U7XRE6AXLKI/</a>"},{"pid":"90067a0663e25ab6da72ec3b7f43778b87a711b8","tid":2463640,"uid":308251,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T01:11:36.000Z","msg":"對比香港，香港真係多人血饅頭食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc1947c7b89d1913759902c0019d3679bdb3a2d","tid":2463640,"uid":88629,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90067a0663e25ab6da72ec3b7f43778b87a711b8","tid":2463640,"uid":308251,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T01:11:36.000Z","msg":"對比香港，香港真係多人血饅頭食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T01:15:20.000Z","msg":"兩者有關係？對比到啲乜？"},{"pid":"351c4743e8cadc0e7f35c002dc1af26b36b91af4","tid":2463640,"uid":282494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T01:21:19.000Z","msg":"英美又係做門面功夫<br />\n不痛不癢"},{"pid":"3f80d8c1590bd280fd6f134d2ba9a713ce9ea485","tid":2463640,"uid":4180,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"90067a0663e25ab6da72ec3b7f43778b87a711b8","tid":2463640,"uid":308251,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T01:11:36.000Z","msg":"對比香港，香港真係多人血饅頭食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T01:22:41.000Z","msg":"對比香港，香港真係多分化撚，內鬥撚"},{"pid":"6b2f9a0cceda8a84738cd9d33ef9fe1e17ef64d4","tid":2463640,"uid":3860,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"6dc1947c7b89d1913759902c0019d3679bdb3a2d","tid":2463640,"uid":88629,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90067a0663e25ab6da72ec3b7f43778b87a711b8","tid":2463640,"uid":308251,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T01:11:36.000Z","msg":"對比香港，香港真係多人血饅頭食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T01:15:20.000Z","msg":"兩者有關係？對比到啲乜？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T01:28:52.000Z","msg":"standard script 黎<br />\n<br />\n成個弱智咁個個post 都留句黃店，人血饅頭<br />\n好撚低質<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c64a0515ff905ac6b41b4837c6326da1add44b3","tid":2463640,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T01:35:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9e0ae2d400b71c1f721a8fb634da4b1707c3f21","tid":2463640,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6dc1947c7b89d1913759902c0019d3679bdb3a2d","tid":2463640,"uid":88629,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90067a0663e25ab6da72ec3b7f43778b87a711b8","tid":2463640,"uid":308251,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T01:11:36.000Z","msg":"對比香港，香港真係多人血饅頭食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T01:15:20.000Z","msg":"兩者有關係？對比到啲乜？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T02:13:05.000Z","msg":"一邊就拎啲人血黎整饅頭，一邊就拎啲人血去繼續爭取民主，咁講應該比較清楚啦下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4acf6edf24ff51c1b1c798a29531fd6a0b61589c","tid":2463640,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b2f9a0cceda8a84738cd9d33ef9fe1e17ef64d4","tid":2463640,"uid":3860,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"6dc1947c7b89d1913759902c0019d3679bdb3a2d","tid":2463640,"uid":88629,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90067a0663e25ab6da72ec3b7f43778b87a711b8","tid":2463640,"uid":308251,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T01:11:36.000Z","msg":"對比香港，香港真係多人血饅頭食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T01:15:20.000Z","msg":"兩者有關係？對比到啲乜？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T01:28:52.000Z","msg":"standard script 黎<br />\n<br />\n成個弱智咁個個post 都留句黃店，人血饅頭<br />\n好撚低質<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T02:15:52.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"gold\">2.）</span>另外，佢哋亦會<span class=\"red\">熱狗式放負</span>，無論你做乜佢地都會揾到嘢鬧，最好乜都唔好做，因為唔做就自然唔會出錯，正正因為咩都唔做，正合極權所需，而如果真係咩都唔做，佢哋又會笑你咩都唔做輸啦輸啦，雞蛋挑骨頭就係熱狗式放負嘅一大特色<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>而其實所謂踩港撚九成都係五毛（其餘一成就係弱智跟風on9）目的旨在消滅香港人對自己嘅自信、自豪感、優越感，同埋對彼此嘅感情，製造互不信任、互相猜疑、自暴自棄嘅氛圍，從而穩定政權。以下現象為其中一個表徵：<br />\n<br />\n大家有冇發現，連登總係有一班人，無論你做啲咩嘢，都可以有位話到你，一日到黑不斷講輸啦輸啦冇人做嘢啦，你唔做嘢佢地會話香港人係奴隸係抵死係癈柴，你去做佢地會話得雞水咁小力有咩用呀邊夠人鬥呀，不如放棄啦做隻港豬算啦，當社會上有一大班人去做嘅時候佢地就會笑你係送頭係戇鳩，跟住就會講人地食花生睇戲呀你地就繼續做傻仔幫港豬移民走啦之類嘅說話內容。佢地真係同路人？大家試諗下，如果真係手足係會俾建議幫手補鑊，即使有唔同意見亦唔會淨係留言不斷笑香港人送頭嘅撚樣，冷嘲熱諷撚一黎只會對件事無幫助，二黎只會散播失敗風同打擊士氣，<span class=\"red\"><strong>令人遺憾嘅係有唔少傻仔上咗呢一班人嘅當連自己都講埋一份。</strong></span>呢一班究竟係咩人，自己諗。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n（依照經驗所得，發現<span class=\"red\">呢類人未必係五毛但可能係思維唔發達而周圍放負嘅on9</span>，正正係因為自己解答唔到革命難題，又想急功近利，提出一啲不切實際嘅要求（eg. 200萬人勇武，放諸全世界嘅stat都係冇可能）。當人哋解釋完/ 鬧完自己又駁唔到，但又接受唔到人地批評自己，老羞成怒，開始一味笑人「一講乜乜就屌人乜乜」，<span class=\"gold\">最後變成一個好嬲好嬲，然後上連登笑人好嬲好嬲嘅冷氣軍師</span>，從中獲得「眾人皆醉我獨醒」嘅心理優越&amp;安慰感。由呢一刻開始，思維因心態而扭曲，言論亦變成放負為主而無實質上嘅建議，呢類人即使本身唔係五毛，但行徑上已經同五毛無異。）<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">For example:</span><br />\n<br />\n五毛/ 弱能思維on9：<br />\n1.）繼續快樂抗爭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你班廢柴剩係買嘢就可以打倒共產黨啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.）成班和理非去shopping 就當自己出咗一份力，當手足condom <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.）叫你衝又唔敢衝學咩人搞革命呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dd2de25ee1c6f6c4040728109da452475191786","tid":2463640,"uid":327169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T02:16:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d1e4170992a480bca750e93b2f95b6d65fc684","tid":2463640,"uid":34755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T02:17:00.000Z","msg":"打內戰算啦"}]}